## 🚀 Project Overview  
Forensic 360 provides an intuitive and **secure forensic data management system** that allows users to:  
✅ **Authenticate securely** using Firebase Authentication  
✅ **Upload & analyze forensic evidence** such as images, videos, and documents  
✅ **Store & manage evidence** securely using Firebase Firestore  
✅ **Generate detailed forensic reports** for case analysis  

This project aims to **streamline forensic investigations** by providing a **centralized, scalable, and efficient solution** for forensic experts.  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack  

| Component   | Technology Used |
|------------|----------------|
| **Backend** | FastAPI (Python) |
| **Frontend** | React (JavaScript) |
| **Database** | Firebase Firestore & Firebase Storage |
| **Authentication** | Firebase Auth |
| **Hosting** | Firebase Hosting / Vercel |

